summary: nothing special just op daedric gear
descriptionHtml: This mod adds an alter of molag bal with a chest of op daedric gear to helgen keep in the corner of the room by the last bed (idk if i messed up the lighting or its one of my mods i have on but i couldnt see where the alter and chest were, may add some red spooky lighting). You must follow hadvar to acquire the gear ( might make it so you can get it if you follow ralof if people ask.) I may also add an enchanted version in the future.
